                    <p>Partnered with Tuffyhealth in 2020 after leaving his teaching career</p>
                    <p>DrMehdi@tuffyhealth.com</p>
                    <p><button class="button">Contact</button></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


